  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nI.e. when validating file-based templates. Currently, Qute only considers the default sections and [unknown sections are simply ignored](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/2.15.3.Final/extensions/qute/deployment/src/main/java/io/quarkus/qute/deployment/QuteProcessor.java#L480-L493).\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nWe could introduce a new annotation (e.g. `@RegisterSectionHelperFactory`)  declared on a `io.quarkus.qute.SectionHelperFactory` implementation with a no-args constructor. And then (1) instantiate this factory during validation and (2) instantiate and [register the factory automatically at runtime](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/2.15.3.Final/extensions/qute/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/qute/runtime/EngineProducer.java#L159). ",
